    "long_instructions": "## Finish the Sentence\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to finish the sentence.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Think about how you would complete the following sentence: *\"The dog barked at the...\"*\r\n2. **Copy and paste** the following prompt: \r\n\r\n>Complete this sentence: The dog barked at the...\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. Then read **AI Chat's response** and compare it to your own.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n:::details [**Want to try another prompt?**]\r\n\r\nCome up with a sentence of your own and see how AI chooses to finish it. Some examples:\r\n> I'm excited to learn how to...\r\n\r\n> What I really want for my birthday is...\r\n:::",
